f fitness, maximal ??̇ ??2. The results showed the strong ability of the proposed algorithms to predict ??̇ ??2 during ?????? based on wearable sensors allowing for not only overall assessment of metabolic rate but also for successful prediction of ??̇ ??2 dynamics. Thus, the proposed ??̇ ??2 predictor in conjunction with ?????? can be used to investigate aerobic fitness during ?????? with direct applicability for the general population. This new technology provides a significant advance in ambulatory and continuous assessment of aerobic fitness with potential for future applications such as the early detection of deterioration in physical health},
